object.customQuery:
select prsn_intn_id, plan_ky, rep_beg_dt, rep_end_dt, case when rnum=1 then date('2299-12-31') else prev_date  end as act_rep_end_dt from (
select prsn_intn_id, clnt_ky, plan_ky, rep_beg_dt, rep_end_dt, dateadd(day,-1,(max(rep_beg_dt) over (partition by clnt_ky, prsn_intn_id, plan_ky order by rep_beg_dt desc rows between 1 preceding and current row))) as prev_date, 
row_number() over (partition by clnt_ky, prsn_intn_id, plan_ky order by rep_beg_dt desc)  as rnum from healthsa_rpt.acct_bal_prcs_fact where rep_beg_dt> rep_end_dt and 1=0 ) t1

       Max(rlvr_at)            AS rlvr_at,

       Max(clm_pmt_at)         AS clm_pmt_at, 
       Max(chk_rcvy_at)        AS chk_rcvy_at, 
       Max(onln_rcvy_at)       AS onln_rcvy_at, 
       Max(clm_paid_at)        AS clm_paid_at, 
       Max(opmt_at)            AS opmt_at, 
       Max(clm_rcvy_at)        AS clm_rcvy_at, 
       Max(tot_rcvy_at)        AS tot_rcvy_at,

       plan_ky, 
       Max(prsn_addr_ky)       AS prsn_addr_ky, 
       Max(clm_paid_at_n_insu) AS CLM_PAID_AT_N_INSU, 
       Max(rqst_at)            AS rqst_at, 
       Max(elig_at)            AS elig_at, 
       cal_dt , 
       Max(plan_yy_stat_cd)    AS plan_yy_stat_cd,

       Max(ctrb_fl)            AS ctrb_fl, 
       Max(plan_max)           AS plan_max, 
       Max(clnt_ky)            AS clnt_ky, 
       Max(plan_typ_cd)        AS plan_typ_cd, 
       Max(clm_rcvr_anthr_yy)  AS CLM_RCVR_ANTHR_YY, 
       Max(high_cv_at)         AS HIGH_CV_AT, 
       MAX(cv_end_dt) AS cv_end_dt ,
	   MAX(CRVR_AT) AS CRVR_AT,
	   max(rlvr_gnrc_prvs_id) as rlvr_gnrc_prvs_id,
	   max(BRK_IN_CV_RLVR_CD) as BRK_IN_CV_RLVR_CD
FROM   (SELECT A.ee_ctrb_at, 
               A.er_ctrb_at, 
               A.excs_ctrb_at, 
               A.tot_ctrb_at, 
               A.intr_at, 
               A.earn_at, 
               A.rlvr_at, 
               A.rlvr_used_at, 
               A.clm_pmt_at, 
               A.chk_rcvy_at, 
               A.onln_rcvy_at,

               A.prsn_addr_ky,

               A.rqst_at, 
               A.elig_at, 
               B.cal_dt, 
               C.plan_yy_stat_cd, 
               C.cv_fl, 
               C.ctrb_fl, 
               C.plan_max, 
               C.clnt_ky, 
               C.plan_typ_cd,
               c.rlvr_gnrc_prvs_id, 
c.BRK_IN_CV_RLVR_CD,
               Coalesce(CLM.clm_rcvr_anthr_yy, 0) AS CLM_RCVR_ANTHR_YY, 
               Coalesce(e.high_cv_at, 0)         AS HIGH_CV_AT, 
               coalesce(D.cv_end_dt,'2299-12-31') AS cv_end_dt,
A.CRVR_AT_CT AS CRVR_AT
        FROM   healthsa_rpt.acct_trnsprcs_fact A 
               INNER JOIN healthsa_rpt.plan_dimn C 
               ON A.plan_ky = C.plan_ky 
             LEFT JOIN (
SELECT MAX(cv_end_dt) AS cv_end_dt,prsn_intn_id ,plan_ky FROM healthsa_rpt.CV_FACT
where CV_AT<>0.00    
GROUP BY PRSN_INTN_ID,PLAN_KY  

)D
               ON        D.prsn_intn_id = A.prsn_intn_id 
                       AND D.PLAN_KY = C.PLAN_KY 
inner JOIN (SELECT MAX(cv_at) AS high_cv_at,prsn_intn_id AS prsn_intn_id,plan_ky AS plan_ky FROM healthsa_rpt.acct_trnsprcs_fact          
GROUP BY PRSN_INTN_ID,PLAN_KY  )e
               ON        e.prsn_intn_id = A.prsn_intn_id 
                       AND e.plan_ky = A.plan_ky
               INNER JOIN healthsa_rpt.date_dimn B 
                       ON A.trns_dt_ky = B.date_ky 
               LEFT JOIN (SELECT prsn_intn_id, 
                                 plan_ky, 
                                 prcs_dt_ky, 
                                 Sum(clm_rcvy_an_yy_at) AS CLM_RCVR_ANTHR_YY 
                          FROM   healthsa_rpt.clm_pmt_fact 
                          WHERE  clm_rcvy_an_yy_at != 0 
                          GROUP  BY prsn_intn_id, 
                                    plan_ky, 
                                    prcs_dt_ky)CLM 
                      ON A.prsn_intn_id = CLM.prsn_intn_id 
                         AND A.plan_ky = CLM.plan_ky 
                         AND A.trns_dt_ky = CLM.prcs_dt_ky 
) FACT       
GROUP  BY FACT.prsn_intn_id, 
          FACT.plan_ky, 
          cal_dt ) aa
               INNER JOIN healthsa_rpt.PLAN_DIMN C 
                       ON Aa.plan_ky = C.plan_ky 
left outer join healthsa_ctd.EE_EMPL_CAT_SH empl
on aa.PRSN_INTN_ID = empl.PRSN_INTN_ID
and EMPL.EMPL_CAT_ID='5740'
and aa.cal_dt between EMPL.EE_EMPLCAT_EFBEGDT and EMPL.EE_EMPLCAT_EFENDDT
left outer join healthsa_ctd.EE_EMPL_CAT_SH empl1
on aa.PRSN_INTN_ID = empl1.PRSN_INTN_ID
and EMPL1.EMPL_CAT_ID='1'
and aa.cal_dt between EMPL1.EE_EMPLCAT_EFBEGDT and EMPL1.EE_EMPLCAT_EFENDDT
INNER JOIN healthsa_rpt.PLAN_DIMN PLDIM
ON aa.plan_ky=pldim.plan_ky 
left outer join healthsa_ctd.prsn_saa_cv_sh f
on aa.PRSN_INTN_ID=f.PRSN_INTN_ID
and pldim.plan_id=f.Plan_id
and aa.cal_dt >= f.EFBEGDT and aa.cal_dt <= f.EFENDDT
               INNER JOIN healthsa_rpt.date_dimn B 
                       ON Aa.cal_dt = B.cal_dt 
left outer join healthsa_rpt.cv_fact f1
on aa.PRSN_INTN_ID=f1.PRSN_INTN_ID
and pldim.PLAN_KY=f1.PLAN_KY
AND B.cal_dt >= f1.cv_beg_dt AND (B.cal_dt <= f1.cv_end_dt)
               LEFT outer JOIN healthsa_rpt.cv_fact CV 
                      ON aa.prsn_intn_id = CV.prsn_intn_id 
                         AND aa.plan_ky = CV.plan_ky 
                        AND (B.cal_dt BETWEEN CV.cv_beg_dt AND CV.cv_end_dt) 
               LEFT outer JOIN healthsa_rpt.cv_fact CV3 
                      ON aa.prsn_intn_id = CV3.prsn_intn_id 
                         AND aa.plan_ky = CV3.plan_ky 
                        AND (c.PLAN_YY_END_DT BETWEEN CV3.cv_beg_dt AND CV3.cv_end_dt) 
LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT prsn_intn_id,plan_ky,BB.cal_dt FROM healthsa_rpt.prsn_rlvr_fact RF
                      INNER JOIN healthsa_rpt.date_dimn BB 
                       ON RF.SRC_DT_KY = BB.DATE_KY)  RL 
                           ON RL.prsn_intn_id=aa.prsn_intn_id
                          and RL.plan_ky=aa.plan_ky
                          and RL.cal_dt=aa.cal_dt 
) a

left outer join
(

select eec.prsn_intn_id, eec.ee_emplcat_efbegdt, eec.ee_emplcat_efenddt,spys.plan_yy_efbegdt
, nvl(cgcs.cat_cd,'NOT_ELIG') as cat_cd from 
healthsa_ctd.ee_empl_cat_sh eec
inner join healthsa_ctd.prsn_sh pr
on pr.prsn_intn_id= eec.prsn_intn_id
inner join (select distinct em_clnt_id,rlvr_gnrc_prvs_id, plan_yy_efbegdt from healthsa_ctd.saa_pln_yy_stat_sh where rlvr_cd='Y') spys
on spys.em_clnt_id= pr.em_clnt_id
and (eec.ee_emplcat_efbegdt between spys.plan_yy_efbegdt and Dateadd(day,-1,Dateadd(year,1,spys.plan_yy_efbegdt))
or eec.ee_emplcat_efenddt between spys.plan_yy_efbegdt and Dateadd(day,-1,Dateadd(year,1,spys.plan_yy_efbegdt)))
left outer join healthsa_ctd.gnrc_id_gp gig
on gig.gp_id= spys.rlvr_gnrc_prvs_id
left outer join healthsa_ctd.saa_rlvr_rule_sh srrs
on srrs.saa_rlvr_rule_id= gig.gnrc_id
left outer join healthsa_ctd.cat_gp_sh cg
on cg.gp_id= srrs.rlvr_elig_gp_id
left outer join healthsa_ctd.cat_gp_cd_sh cgcs 
on cgcs.gp_id= cg.gp_id
and eec.empl_stat_cd= cgcs.cat_cd
where
eec.empl_cat_id= cg.cat_id
and cgcs.cat_cd is null

) check_elig
on check_elig.prsn_intn_id=a.prsn_intn_id 
and a.cal_dt between check_elig.EE_EMPLCAT_EFBEGDT and check_elig.EE_EMPLCAT_EFENDDT

where  
(a.prsn_intn_id, 
a.plan_ky,a.cal_dt)
not in (select prf.prsn_intn_id, prf.plan_ky, dd.cal_dt from healthsa_rpt.prsn_rlvr_fact prf
inner join healthsa_rpt.plan_dimn pd
on prf.plan_ky= pd.plan_ky
inner join healthsa_rpt.date_dimn dd
on dd.cal_dt= pd.plan_yy_end_dt
where (pd.plan_id = 5710 or (pd.plan_id = 5720 and pd.clnt_ky = 109086))
and (dd.date_ky)= prf.src_dt_ky
and (prf.prsn_intn_id, prf.plan_ky, prf.rlvr_at) in ( select tab1.prsn_intn_id, tab1.plan_ky, tab1.rlvr_at from (
select distinct p1.*, count(prsn_intn_id) over(partition by prsn_intn_id, plan_ky, rlvr_at) as cnt from healthsa_rpt.prsn_rlvr_fact p1) tab1
where tab1.cnt>1) )
ORDER  BY a.prsn_intn_id, 
a.plan_ky,
         a.PLAN_YY_END_DT,
          a.cal_dt asc

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

fields.name: LTST_CV_AT1
fields.expression:
IIF(plan_id =5710 , IIF(cal_dt>cv_end_dt
AND 
cv_end_dt<>PLAN_YY_END_DT,0.00,LTST_CV_AT),
IIF(cal_dt>cv_end_dt
and EMPL_STAT_CD='N'
AND
INTR_FL='N',0.00,LTST_CV_AT))

fields.name: V_RLVR_AT
fields.expression:
IIF(ROW_EXIST='Y' ,iif(Exp_cat_cd<>'NOT_ELIG', iif( PREV_RLVR_AT<>Exp_RLVR_AT
and Exp_RLVR_AT  != 0 , Exp_RLVR_AT , PREV_RLVR_AT),0),Exp_RLVR_AT)

fields.name: V_CRVR_AT
fields.expression:
IIF(ROW_EXIST='Y' ,iif( PREV_CRVR_AT<>Exp_CRVR_AT
and Exp_CRVR_AT  != 0 , Exp_CRVR_AT , PREV_CRVR_AT),Exp_CRVR_AT)
--IIF(ROW_EXIST='Y',PREV_RLVR_AT + RLVR_AT,RLVR_AT)

fields.name: O_TOT_FND_AT
fields.expression:
IIF(Exp_cal_dt>Exp_cv_end_dt
and v_LASTDAY_OF_YEAR = 'N'
and Exp_cv_at2=0.00
and Exp_plan_id <>5710
and Exp_plan_id <>9100
and ( Exp_EMPL_STAT_CD='N'
OR
Exp_INTR_FL='N' OR isNull(Exp_INTR_FL) OR isNull(Exp_EMPL_STAT_CD) OR Exp_INTR_FL='' OR Exp_EMPL_STAT_CD='')
and ((Exp_rlvr_gnrc_prvs_id = 0 and Exp_brk_in_cv_rlvr_cd <>'Y') or (Exp_rlvr_gnrc_prvs_id > 0 and Exp_cat_cd = 'NOT_ELIG'))
,0.00,
IIF(
(TO_CHAR(Exp_cv_end_dt,'YYYY-MM-DD') = 
'1800-01-01'),0,V_TOT_FND_AT
))

fields.name: O_AVLB_BAL_AT
fields.expression:
IIF(Exp_cal_dt>Exp_cv_end_dt
and v_LASTDAY_OF_YEAR = 'N'
and Exp_cv_at2=0.00
